title: Carl & Jackie - Part 2: The Triggermen (Carl Gaimari)
description:
Arson, adultery and a wife under arrest for orchestrating her husband’s murder. Investigators know the puppet master, but who were the puppets?

For episode information and photos, please visit https://anatomyofmurder.com/.
